high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the spatula from the back of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the spatula inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, head left to the counter and face the counter to the left.
Put the rinsed spatula in front of the pan in the middle of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spatula on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and make a left to walk towards the far counter.
Pick up the spatula from the countertop.
Make a left and walk back towards the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Make a right to face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Place the spatula down on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spatula to put it on the countertop next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you near the wall.
Turn around and walk to the sink then turn right when you get to it.
Wash the spatula in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and take a step then turn left and take a small step back.
Put the spatula under the frying pan near the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the counter.
